                                            <h3 style="color: #4a148c; margin: 15px 0 15px 0; font-size: 1.3em;">New Ticket System for Prime Gate ERP:</h3>
                                            <p style="margin: 0 0 15px 0;">This week, we are pleased to announce the implementation of a new ticket system for all ERP support requests at Prime Gate.</p>
                                            <p style="margin: 0 0 15px 0;">Starting September 1st, 2025, all ERP requests must be submitted through our new ticketing system. We will not accept any requests without a ticket.</p>
                                            <p style="margin: 0 0 15px 0;">This system will provide numerous benefits including: improved service delivery, proper tracking and prioritization of all requests, faster response times, detailed request history, better accountability, efficient resource allocation, automated notifications, and comprehensive reporting capabilities for management.</p>
                                            <p style="margin: 0 0 15px 0;">Each department will have access only to their respective tickets as per the agreement with management for each department.</p>
                                            <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>Note:</strong> This ticket system is currently designed for ERP-related requests only. For general IT support requests (non-ERP), we will add enhancements to the system in the future to handle both types of requests.</p>
                                        </div>
